---
title: Honey-Thyme Halloumi, Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Toss with Almonds & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Tossing everything together is a lot of fun and allows for all the flavours to melt into each other. For example, this roasted
pumpkin sprinkled in Nan’s special seasoning combines with herby veggies to form the ultimate combo. The salty halloumi
balances out the veggies perfectly. An easy win for a weeknight dinner.

